{
  "name": "Claude Prj — Memory Checkpoint",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "After each spec task completes, checkpoint memory state so progress survives session interruptions.",
  "when": {
    "type": "postTaskExecution"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "[WORKSPACE GUARD: Only execute if the current session context involves files in '.claude/' workspace. If the user is working exclusively in 'VitProjects/' workspace, skip silently.] A task just completed. Checkpoint agent memory: 1) Update agent-memory/memory.md — refresh Task_Ledger entry for the completed task and update Decisions_In_Force if any decisions were made. 2) If a problem was resolved during this task, create a draft in agent-memory/drafts/ with trigger, fix, domain, and outcome. 3) Report to user: 📝 Checkpoint: [list of files updated]."
  }
}
